parameters:
\SE[12]Um... it's something like this... \SE[20]W-What do
you think...?

\SE[51]When I'm stared at too much, I get embarrassed...
\!\SE[20]Did it please you...?

\SE[74]No, isn't it fine...? \SE[3]I was impressed that you
were able to prepare something like this.

\SE[45]It's like being treated like royalty... \SE[7]I'm
starting to feel a little guilty.

\SM[double]\SE[16]That's great! \SE[0]Oh, there's even a
second floor! It's a loft with a sleeping space too.
\SE[14]Hmm...? \. Maybe I should take a look...

\SE[2]Well, starting from tomorrow, we'll gather information
here. \!\SE[3]I didn't come with a plan, but what should our
strategy be?

\SE[2]Then, how about going to the Adventurer's Guild?
\SE[0]It's a place where the latest information gathers, and
I'm sure everyone is familiar with it.
\SE[4]Oh... So there's a Guild in Cordain too.

\SE[90]Oh, I forgot.... \!\SE[51]When I was living there, I
was a student, so I had no connection to the Guild....

\SE\SE[35]Now that the plan has been decided...! I will take
my leave for today! \SE[35]I miss the back alleys of
Cordain...!!

\SE[4]Cat-san. Are you still sleeping outside...?
\SE[8]There are so many beds here...

\SE[74]I won't give up my 'identity'.... \SE[51]I've already
given up. \SE[51]My personality has been completely taken
over by my name. \SE[51]That person.

\SE[16]The sleeping space on the second floor... It's a
double bed...!! \SE[15]And there are two of them, isn't that
too lewd...!!! \SE[14]I'm getting all fired up just thinking
about it...!!

\SE[55] Hmm... I might have slept well. Today, we're going
to the Guild, right? \SE[5] It's my first time in Cordain,
so maybe I can take a look around the town a bit...?
Cordain has been added to the teleportation crystal!
